title: I-30 Dallas Lake Ray Hubbard Crossing Construction

pageHeader.title: I-30 Dallas Lake Ray Hubbard Crossing Construction

text: This project adds frontage roads to the Lake Ray Hubbard crossing.

images.caption: This view looks west on the south side of the crossing, showing construction of the eastbound frontage road.
Looking east from the west end of the crossing, near Bass Pro Shops
View from the west end near Bass Pro Shops
Service vessels at the west end.
On the east end, piers for the connector ramp to Dalrock Road.
In April 2023 the eastbound frontage road was nearing completion.
